general.desc: NetX Holdings Bhd is an investment holding company. It operates in the segments: Electronic payment services and software licensing that involves the terminal, software licensing, and other services; Non-electronic payment services involves provision of turnkey solutions on the network infrastructure, security management, research and development of software, system design, integration and installation and provision of information technology services; GEM involves provision of reservation and planning services and related solutions; Money Lending Services provides money lending business, trading of motor vehicle and related service; Fast Food Chain operates fast food restaurants and master franchise of fast food chain and Others. The company derives its revenue from Malaysia.
